232.description: +0.3 speed. Automatically inflicts slow to all enemies in every room. +0.3 speed. Upon taking damage, inflicts slow to all enemies for the current room. +0.3 speed. Slows all enemies in every room to 80% speed.
232.quote: Let's slow this down a bit...

233.name: Tiny Planet
233.description: Massively increases Range and grants spectral tears. Tears orbit around Isaac at a fixed distance until they hit the ground.

234.name: Infestation 2
234.description: Spawns allied Blue Spiders from killed enemies.

236.name: E. Coli
236.description: Enemies that touch Isaac are transformed into Poop.

237.name: Death's Touch
237.description: +1.5 damage, -0.3 tears. Tears are replaced with large piercing scythes.

238.name: Key Piece 1
238.description: Combined with Key Piece 2, unlocks the golden gate in the starting room of Chest and Dark Room to fight Mega Satan.

239.name: Key Piece 2
239.description: Combined with Key Piece 1, unlocks the golden gate in the starting room of Chest and Dark Room to fight Mega Satan.

240.name: Experimental Treatment
240.description: Randomly increases and decreases some of Isaac's stats. Increases four random stats and decreases the other two.
240.quote: Some stats up, some stats down

241.name: Contract From Below
241.description: Doubles the number of most room clear awards, but reduces the overall chance of getting one by 1/3.

242.name: Infamy
242.description: Gives Isaac a 50% chance to block projectiles coming from any direction.

243.name: Trinity Shield
243.description: Isaac gains a shield that protects him from enemy shots. It aims in the direction Isaac fires from.

244.name: Tech.5
244.description: Isaac occasionally fires an unlimited range piercing laser alongside his normal tears. The laser can glitch, mimicking the effects of certain items and trinkets.

245.description: Isaac fires two tears at once, one from each eye. 0.8× damage multiplier.

246.name: Blue Map
246.description: Reveals the locations of Secret Rooms and Super Secret Rooms on the map.

247.name: BFFS!
247.description: Increases the size and effectiveness of most familiars.

248.name: Hive Mind
248.description: Increases the size of Blue Spiders and Blue Flies and doubles the amount of damage they deal. Also increases the effectiveness of fly and spider familiars.

249.name: There's Options
249.description: Two items appear after defeating a Boss. Only one can be taken; the other will disappear.

250.name: BOGO Bombs
250.description: All normal Bombs become Double Bombs.

251.name: Starter Deck
251.description: Isaac can hold 2 cards at once and all pills are replaced by cards.

252.name: Little Baggy
252.description: Isaac can hold 2 pills at once and all cards and runes are replaced by pills.

253.name: Magic Scab
253.description: Grants one full Red Heart container, +1 luck. Heals 1 additional Red Heart.

254.name: Blood Clot
254.description: Tears fired from the left eye have +1 flat damage, +5 range, and +0.5 tear falling speed. Tears fired from the left eye have +1 flat damage and +2.75 range.

256.name: Hot Bombs
256.description: +5 Bombs. Isaac's bombs leave behind fire that damages enemies upon contact.

257.name: Fire Mind
257.description: Grants flaming tears that deal burning damage over time. Tears have a chance to explode on impact with an enemy, which creates a fire at the location of the explosion.

258.name: Missing No.
258.description: Randomizes all passive items and stats upon pickup and at the start of each succeeding floor.

259.name: Dark Matter
259.description: +1 damage, adds a chance to shoot fear tears.

260.name: Black Candle
260.description: Prevents curses. Grants one Black Heart. Increases the chance for a Devil Room or Angel Room to appear.

261.name: Proptosis
261.description: Tears start out massive with high damage, and then shrink down and become weaker over a short range.

262.name: Missing Page 2
262.description: Grants one Black Heart. Upon taking damage that reduces Isaac's health to one heart or less, deals damage to all enemies in the room. Increases the damage of Black Hearts and The Necronomicon -like effects by 40.
262.quote: Evil up. Your enemies will pay!

263.name: Clear Rune
263.description: Has the same effect as the rune or soul stone currently held by Isaac. The charge time is based on the power of the rune.

264.name: Smart Fly
264.description: Spawns an orbital familiar that blocks enemy shots. Upon taking damage, the familiar will pursue enemies for the rest of the room, dealing 22.5 damage per second.

265.name: Dry Baby
265.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac around and blocks enemy projectiles. Upon blocking a shot, it has a chance of triggering The Necronomicon effect.

266.name: Juicy Sack
266.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac and drips a trail of slow creep, spawning 1-2 Blue Spiders after each room.

267.name: Robo-Baby 2.0
267.description: Spawns a familiar that fires lasers at any enemy in its line of sight and moves based on the direction Isaac is firing tears.
267.quote: We worked out all the kinks

268.name: Rotten Baby
268.description: Spawns a familiar that spawns a Blue Fly when Isaac shoots. It can only have one Fly at a time.

269.name: Headless Baby
269.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac, leaving blood creep on the ground.

270.name: Leech
270.description: Spawns a leech familiar that chases enemies, dealing ~3 damage per second. Heals a Half Red Heart whenever Leech kills an enemy.

271.name: Mystery Sack
271.description: Spawns a familiar that drops a Heart, coin, Bomb, or Key every 5-6 rooms.

272.name: BBF
272.description: Spawns a familiar that flies around the room in a zig-zag pattern and explodes on contact with an enemy. Respawns after ten seconds.

273.name: Bob's Brain
273.description: Spawns a familiar that charges forward when shooting tears and explodes upon contact with an enemy, damaging and poisoning them. The familiar respawns after a few seconds.

274.name: Best Bud
274.description: When hit, spawns a quickly orbiting attack fly similar to Forever Alone for the current room that deals high damage.

275.name: Lil Brimstone
275.description: Grants a familiar that charges a thin Brimstone laser while Isaac is shooting.

276.name: Isaac's Heart
276.description: Isaac himself is now immune to all damage, and a heart familiar follows him. If the heart is hurt, Isaac is hurt. The heart charges up as Isaac shoots, firing 8 blood shots, knocking back enemies, and leaving a puddle of creep when released.

277.name: Lil Haunt
277.description: Spawns a familiar that chases down enemies, dealing 4 damage per second and inflicting fear.

278.name: Dark Bum
278.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac around and collects Red Hearts. For every 1½ Red Hearts collected, Dark Bum will give a reward.
278.quote: He wants to take your life

279.name: Big Fan
279.description: Spawns a large orbital familiar that blocks enemy shots and deals 30 damage per second to enemies.

280.name: Sissy Longlegs
280.description: Spawns a familiar that wanders randomly, occasionally spawning Blue Spiders. Briefly charms enemies on contact.

281.name: Punching Bag
281.description: Spawns a Mulligan familiar that wanders randomly. Enemies will attack the Mulligan if it's closer.

282.name: How to Jump
282.description: Isaac jumps in the direction he is currently moving, allowing travel over obstacles and enemies.

283.name: D100
283.description: Combines the effects of D4, The D6, and D20. Combines the effects of D1, D4, The D6, D7, D8, D10, D12, and D20.

284.name: D4
284.description: Rerolls all of Isaac's passive items.

285.name: D10
285.description: Re-rolls all monsters in the room. Replaces all monsters in the room with weaker monsters.

286.name: Blank Card
286.description: Copies the effect of the card or rune currently held by Isaac. Copies the effect of the card currently held by Isaac. The charge time is based on the power of the card.

287.name: Book of Secrets
287.description: Gives the effect of Treasure Map, The Compass, or Blue Map for the duration of the current floor. If all effects are active, X-Ray Vision is provided for the floor instead. Highlights any Tinted Rocks and rocks with Crawl Space in the room.

288.name: Box of Spiders
288.description: Spawns 1-4 Blue Spiders that deal 2.5× Isaac's damage to enemies. Spawns 4-8 Blue Spiders that deal 2× Isaac's damage to enemies.

289.name: Red Candle
289.description: Throws out a flame that damages everything in its path, diminishing in size as it hits enemies or blocks shots.

290.name: The Jar
290.description: When at full health, up to 4 extra Red Hearts can be stored in The Jar. Activating drops the stored hearts on the ground.

291.name: Flush!
291.description: Turns all non-boss monsters in the room into Poop. Instantly kills poop-themed bosses. Floods the current room.

292.name: Satanic Bible
292.description: Gives one Black Heart. Replaces the boss room item on the current floor with a Devil Deal.
292.quote: Reusable evil... but at what cost?

293.name: Head of Krampus
293.description: Fires a powerful Brimstone beam in four cardinal directions, much like Krampus shoots. Fires a powerful Brimstone beam in four cardinal directions, much like Krampus shoots with a 50% chance to rotate all beams around Isaac 90 degrees.

294.name: Butter Bean
294.description: Isaac farts and knocks back nearby enemies and projectiles. Enemies pushed into walls or obstacles take 12 damage.

295.name: Magic Fingers
295.description: Uses 1 Penny to deal damage to all enemies in the room.

296.name: Converter
296.description: Converts two Soul Hearts or Black Hearts into one filled Red Heart Container. Converts one Soul Heart or Black Heart into one filled Red Heart Container.

297.name: Pandora's Box
297.description: Spawns specific pickups or items depending on the floor it is used on. Disappears after use.

298.name: Unicorn Stump
298.description: Gives invulnerability and increased speed for six seconds, but removes the ability to shoot tears.

299.name: Taurus
299.description: -0.3 Speed. Isaac builds speed while in a room with enemies. At max speed, he gains the My Little Unicorn effect for 5 seconds.

300.name: Aries
300.description: +0.25 Speed. Running into enemies while at a high speed will deal damage. Prevents Isaac from taking contact damage while moving at high speed.

301.name: Cancer
301.description: Adds 3 Soul Hearts. Grants The Wafer effect for the current room after taking damage.

302.name: Leo
302.description: Isaac can destroy rocks by walking into them.

303.name: Virgo
303.description: Adds a chance to give a shield that nullifies all incoming damage for 10 seconds upon taking damage. Also converts bad pills into good pills.

304.name: Libra
304.description: Gives 6 Coins, 6 Bombs, and 6 Keys and balances out all attributes.

305.name: Scorpio
305.description: Grants poison tears, which deal damage over time when inflicted.

306.name: Sagittarius
306.description: Increases speed by +0.2 and grants piercing tears.

307.name: Capricorn
307.description: Adds 1 Red Heart Container, gives +0.5 Damage, +0.1 Speed, +1.5 Range, and -1.0 Tear Delay, and gives 1 Bomb, Penny, and Key. Adds 1 Red Heart Container, gives +0.5 Damage, +0.1 Speed, +0.75 Range, and +0.5 Fire Rate, and gives 1 Bomb, Penny, and Key.

308.name: Aquarius
308.description: A trail of blue creep is left behind Isaac, which damages enemies. The creep inherits most of Isaac's tear effects, like homing, etc.

309.name: Pisces
309.description: -1 Tear Delay, adds knock-back shots and increases tear size. +0.5 Fire Rate, adds knock-back shots and increases tear size.

310.name: Eve's Mascara
310.description: Doubles damage, halves tears stat, and greatly reduces shot speed. Doubles damage, 0.66x tears multiplier, and greatly reduces shot speed.
310.quote: DMG up, tears + shot speed down

311.name: Judas' Shadow
311.description: Upon death, respawns Isaac as Dark Judas with two Black Hearts in the previous room.

312.name: Maggy's Bow
312.description: Gives one Red Heart Container and doubles the healing provided by Red Hearts. Also heals 1 Red Heart when obtained.

313.name: Holy Mantle
313.description: Grants a shield that negates the first instance of damage taken from a hostile source once per room.

314.name: Thunder Thighs
314.description: Destroys rocks upon contact with Isaac. Adds one Red Heart container and lowers Speed.
314.quote: HP up + speed down + you feel stompy

315.name: Strange Attractor
315.description: Pickups, trinkets, and monsters are magnetically attracted to Isaac's tears.

316.name: Cursed Eye
316.description: Grants charged tears that can be fired in a tight burst. Getting hit while charging will teleport Isaac to another room.

317.name: Mysterious Liquid
317.description: Tears leave a small, short lasting pool of creep on impact or when their range is depleted.

318.name: Gemini
318.description: Spawns a conjoined familiar which chases enemies close to Isaac, dealing ~6.43 damage per second.

319.name: Cain's Other Eye
319.description: Spawns a familiar that slowly floats around the room on a zig-zag pattern and shoots normal tears in the same direction as Isaac. Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac and fires tears in random cardinal directions that copy Isaac's tears and tear effects and scale with damage.

320.name: ???'s Only Friend
320.description: Spawns a controllable familiar that deals 37.5 damage per second on touch. It can be moved using the shooting directional keys

321.name: Samson's Chains
321.description: Attaches a ball and chain to Isaac that pulls behind him that damages enemies, blocks shots, and destroys most Obstacles.

322.name: Mongo Baby
322.description: Spawns a familiar that copies the tears of Isaac's other familiars.

323.name: Isaac's Tears
323.description: Fires 8 tears around Isaac, which retain the damage, range, shot speed, and special tear effects of his tears. Each tear shot by Isaac increases item charge by one. Tears from this item have a +5 flat damage bonus.

324.name: Undefined
324.description: Teleports Isaac to the Secret Room, Super Secret Room, Treasure Room, or I AM ERROR.

325.name: Scissors
325.description: Turns Isaac's head into a stationary familiar for the current room which fires tears automatically. Isaac's body also shoots a controllable fountain of blood shots for the room.

326.name: Breath of Life
326.description: Grants a brief moment of invincibility when the charge bar hits zero. Isaac begins taking damage if the item is held any longer. Isaac creates beams of light when touching enemies while invulnerable, and creates a powerful 4-way beam if blocking damage exactly as the invincibility starts.

327.name: The Polaroid
327.description: If Isaac has half a red heart or no red hearts after taking damage, he gains a shield that nullifies all types of damage for 5 seconds. Allows entrance into Chest. Also allows access to Home.

328.name: The Negative
328.description: If Isaac has half a red heart or no red hearts after taking damage, all enemies in the room take significant damage. Allows entrance into the Dark Room. +1 Damage and also allows access to Home.

329.name: The Ludovico Technique
329.description: Instead of firing tears, Isaac controls one floating tear that hover over obstacles. This tear deals constant damage when held in place over an enemy.

330.name: Soy Milk
330.description: Tears are smaller and do much less damage, but fire in very rapid succession.

331.name: Godhead
331.description: Grants homing tears with a damaging halo. +0.5 Damage, -0.3 Tears -0.3 Shot Speed, +0.8 Tear Falling Speed, and +1.2 Range. Grants homing tears with a damaging halo. +0.5 Damage, -0.3 Tears, and -0.3 Shot Speed.

332.name: Lazarus' Rags
332.description: Upon dying, resurrect as Lazarus Risen in the current room with one Red Heart container and Anemic. Upon dying, resurrect as Lazarus Risen in the current room with one less Red Heart container, Anemic, and +0.5 Damage. Transform into Lazarus when reaching the next floor.

333.name: The Mind
333.description: Reveals the entire map, including all special rooms and Secret Rooms.

335.name: The Soul
335.description: Grants two Soul Hearts. Isaac gains a pulsing aura that repels enemies and projectiles.

336.name: Dead Onion
336.description: Grants piercing and spectral tears. Increases tear size (without increasing damage) while greatly reducing range and shot speed.

337.name: Broken Watch
337.description: Slows all enemies in every fourth newly-discovered room, with a small chance to speed them up instead.

338.name: The Boomerang
338.description: Throws a boomerang which retrieves pickups, as well as damages and petrifies enemies hit for 2 seconds.

339.name: Safety Pin
339.description: Grants one Black Heart, +5.25 range, +0.5 tear falling speed, +0.16 shot speed. Grants one Black Heart, +2.5 range, +0.16 shot speed.

340.name: Caffeine Pill
340.description: Grants +0.3 speed, reduces Isaac's size, and gives a random pill.

342.name: Blue Cap
342.description: Gives one full Red Heart container, +0.7 tears, and -0.16 shot speed. Heals 1 additional Red Heart.
342.quote: HP + tears up + shot speed down

343.name: Latch Key
343.description: Grants 1 Soul Heart and +1 luck. Spawns 2 Keys.

344.name: Match Book
344.description: Grants Isaac one Black Heart, spawns two or three Bombs. Also spawns Match Stick if it hasn't been encountered yet.

345.name: Synthoil
345.description: +1 damage, +5.25 range, +0.5 tear falling speed. +1 damage, +2.5 range.

346.name: A Snack
346.description: Grants one full Red Heart container. Heals 1 additional Red Heart.

347.name: Diplopia
347.description: Duplicates all pickups and item pedestals in the room.

348.name: Placebo
348.description: Has the same effect as the Pill currently held by Isaac. The charge time is based on the power of the pill.

349.name: Wooden Nickel
349.description: Has a roughly 50% chance to drop a penny, nickel or dime, and a roughly 50% chance to do nothing.

350.name: Toxic Shock
350.description: Upon entering a room, poisons all enemies, dealing double Isaac's tear damage. Killing enemies leaves a small, short-lasting pool of green creep on the ground.

351.name: Mega Bean
351.description: Petrifies all enemies in the current room for about 1.5 seconds, poisons any enemies near Isaac, and sends a rock wave across the room in the direction Isaac is facing.

352.name: Glass Cannon
352.description: Fires a high-damage piercing spectral tear, but lowers Isaac's health to half a heart. Fires a high-damage piercing spectral tear. If Isaac takes damage while holding this, he takes extra damage and it becomes Broken Glass Cannon.

353.name: Bomber Boy
353.description: +5 Bombs. Isaac's bombs will now explode in a large cross-shaped pattern (roughly 5 bombs explosions wide). This also affects player-spawned Troll Bombs.

354.name: Crack Jacks
354.description: Grants one full Red Heart container and drops a random trinket. Heals 1 additional Red Heart.
354.quote: HP up. Don't swallow the prize!

355.name: Mom's Pearls
355.description: +1.25 range, +0.5 tear falling speed, +1 luck. +2.5 range, +1 luck. Grants one Soul Heart.

356.name: Car Battery
356.description: Causes Isaac's activated item to activate twice on each use.

357.name: Box of Friends
357.description: Duplicates all of Isaac's familiars for the current room. If Isaac has no familiars, spawns a Demon Baby for the room instead.

358.name: The Wiz
358.description: Grants spectral tears. Tears simultaneously fire out of both eyes diagonally, similar to the effect of the R U a Wizard? pill.

359.name: 8 Inch Nails
359.description: +1.5 damage. Replaces Isaac's tears with nails, which have increased knockback.

360.name: Incubus
360.description: Spawns a demonic familiar that shoots tears identical to Isaac's in terms of damage, tears, and tear effects.

361.name: Fate's Reward
361.description: A blue head familiar that will follow Isaac and fire tears copying his tear effects and damage.

362.name: Lil Chest
362.description: Spawns a chest familiar that spawns a random pickup (25% chance) or trinket (10% chance) upon clearing a room.

363.name: Sworn Protector
363.description: Spawns an orbital familiar which does 105 damage per second and attracts and blocks enemy shots. Upon blocking 10 shots in a room, it drops an Eternal Heart.

364.name: Friend Zone
364.description: Spawns a white attack fly that orbits somewhere between Distant Admiration and Forever Alone, dealing 45 damage per second.

365.name: Lost Fly
365.description: Spawns fly familiar that moves in a straight line and circles around the first wall or obstacle it hits. It deals 105 damage per second on contact. It deals 56 damage per second and forces nearby enemies to attack it.

366.name: Scatter Bombs
366.description: +5 Bombs. Isaac's bombs explode into 2-4 tiny bombs.
366.quote: We put bombs in your bombs!

367.name: Sticky Bombs
367.description: +5 Bombs. Bombs stick to enemies and spawn 2-4 Blue Spiders if they kill an enemy. They also leave a long-lasting puddle of slowing white creep.

368.name: Epiphora
368.description: Shooting in one direction increases Isaac's rate of fire until the cap is reached. As soon as Isaac changes direction or stops shooting, rate of fire is reset to its normal amount.

369.name: Continuum
369.description: Grants spectral tears and increases range. Tears travel through walls and appear at the opposite side of the room.

370.name: Mr. Dolly
370.description: +0.7 tears, +5.25 range, +0.5 tear falling speed, Spawns a combination of 3 Red Hearts, Soul Hearts or Black Hearts on the floor when picked up. +0.7 tears, +2.5 range, spawns 3 random types of Hearts on the floor when picked up.

371.name: Curse of the Tower
371.description: Upon taking damage, spawns six Troll Bombs around the room, similar to the effect of XVI - The Tower.

372.name: Charged Baby
372.description: Spawns a familiar that occasionally drops a Lil' Battery, gives an active item charge, or petrifies all enemies in the room.

373.name: Dead Eye
373.description: Isaac's damage increases each time an enemy is hit. Damage is reset upon missing a shot.

374.name: Holy Light
374.description: Adds a chance to fire holy tears, which will create a damaging light beam in the area if they hit an enemy.

375.name: Host Hat
375.description: A host familiar that sits on Isaac's head and has a random chance to block enemy shots and retaliate with 3 tears. Grants immunity to explosions.

376.name: Restock
376.description: Causes Shops to instantly restock their items when they are bought. Outside of Greed Mode, the restocked item's cost is increased after each purchase.

377.name: Bursting Sack
377.description: Spider enemies no longer target or deal contact damage to Isaac.

378.name: Number Two
378.description: Continuously firing tears for three seconds causes Isaac to drop a Butt Bomb, which damages and confuses all enemies in the room when it explodes.

379.name: Pupula Duplex
379.description: Gives Isaac spectral tears and gives his tears a wide arc shape, increasing their size.

380.name: Pay To Play
380.description: +5 Coins. Most doors require one Penny to open instead of a Key. +5 Coins. All locked doors, Locked Chests, and Key Blocks must be opened with one Penny instead of Keys.

381.name: Eden's Blessing
381.description: +0.7 tears up. Grants a random item at the start of the next run.
381.quote: Tears up + your future shines brighter

382.name: Friendly Ball
382.description: Throwing the ball at a monster instantly kills and captures it. The captured enemy can later be released and will be friendly, fighting for Isaac and persisting between rooms.

383.name: Tear Detonator
383.description: Splits all of Isaac's tears that are currently in the air into 6 tears that fire in all directions, which retain their damage and shot speed.

384.name: Lil Gurdy
384.description: A Gurdy Jr. familiar that charges up while Isaac is firing, bouncing around the room when released and dealing contact damage based on its speed.

385.name: Bumbo
385.description: Spawns a beggar familiar which picks up any nearby coins, leveling up after collecting several coins. At level 2, Bumbo gains a body. At level 3, it begins to fire tears. At level 4, Bumbo follows enemies and gains contact damage.

386.name: D12
386.description: Re-rolls all Rocks and Metal Blocks in the current room into other random obstacles. Re-rolls most types of Obstacles in the current room into other random obstacles.

387.name: Censer
387.description: Spawns a familiar which creates a circular aura that slows down enemies and enemy shots inside.

388.name: Key Bum
388.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac and collects Keys for himself, giving random Chests in return.

389.name: Rune Bag
389.description: Spawns a familiar that drops a random rune after clearing enough rooms.

390.name: Seraphim
390.description: Spawns an angel familiar who follows Isaac and fires homing tears which deal 10 damage and have 75% shot speed.

391.name: Betrayal
391.description: Charms all enemies in the room when Isaac takes damage. Enemies are able to damage each other. If an enemy is damaged by another enemy, they will attack that enemy instead of Isaac.

392.name: Zodiac
392.description: Gives Isaac a random zodiac item effect that changes every floor.

393.name: Serpent's Kiss
393.description: Tears have a chance to apply a poison effect to enemies. Isaac poisons enemies on contact. Poisoned enemies have a chance to drop a Black Heart when killed.

394.name: Marked
394.description: Isaac will automatically fire tears directed at a red target on the ground. The target can be moved with tear controls. +0.7 tears, increases range.

395.name: Tech X
395.description: Tears are replaced with laser rings that pierce through enemies and deal damage to enemies within them. Can be charged to increase the effectiveness of the ring.

396.name: Ventricle Razor
396.description: Creates up to two portals that remain even if Isaac leaves the room. Upon entering a portal, Isaac is teleported to the other portal.

397.name: Tractor Beam
397.description: Isaac's tears are bound to a beam emitting in the direction he's firing. +0.5 Tears, +5.25 Range, +0.16 Shot Speed. +1 Fire Rate, +2.5 Range, +0.16 Shot Speed.

398.name: God's Flesh
398.description: Tears have a chance to shrink enemies, making them run away from Isaac. Shrunk enemies can be crushed and killed by walking over them.

399.name: Maw Of The Void
399.description: Charged by firing for 2.5 seconds and when released, creates a black ring around Isaac that rapidly deals damage. +1 damage, the ring can cause enemies to drop Black Hearts.

400.name: Spear Of Destiny
400.description: In addition to tears, Isaac holds a spear in front of him which deals contact damage equal to 2x his tear damage, and occasionally inflicts fear.

401.name: Explosivo
401.description: Isaac's tears have a chance to stick to enemies and explode.

402.name: Chaos
402.description: Drops 1-6 random pickups on the floor. Causes items to be chosen from random item pools.

403.name: Spider Mod
403.description: Displays Isaac's tear damage and enemy health bars. Spawns a familiar that wanders around and inflicts random status effects on enemies it touches. Can spawn a Lil' Battery / Blue spider upon clearing a room.

404.name: Farting Baby
404.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac and blocks enemy shots. If a shot hits Farting Baby, it has a chance to fart, which charms, poisons, or knocks back nearby enemies.

405.name: GB Bug
405.description: Spawns a familiar that bounces diagonally around the room, applying a random status effect to enemies it hits and has a chance to re-roll pickups it passes over. Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac. Double tapping the fire button launches it forward, causing it to reroll the first monster or pickup it hits.

406.name: D8
406.description: Re-rolls Isaac's damage, tears, range, and speed.

407.name: Purity
407.description: Boosts one of Isaac's stats depending on the color of the aura around him. The aura disappears upon taking damage and reappears with a random color upon entering a new room. Red boosts damage, blue boosts tears, yellow boosts speed, and orange boosts range.

408.name: Athame
408.description: When Isaac takes damage, a damaging black ring briefly appears around him. This ring can cause enemies to drop Black Hearts. After Isaac kills an enemy, adds a luck -based chance to spawn a damaging black ring around them.

409.name: Empty Vessel
409.description: Grants two Black Hearts. While Isaac has no red hearts, grants flight and periodically grants an invincibility shield for a few seconds.

410.name: Evil Eye
410.description: Adds a chance to fire a slow-moving eye that fires tears in the same direction as Isaac. The eye is destroyed when it hits an enemy or obstacle.

411.name: Lusty Blood
411.description: Isaac's damage increases for the current room each time he kills an enemy.

412.name: Cambion Conception
412.description: After taking damage a certain amount of times, a permanent demonic familiar spawns.

413.name: Immaculate Conception
413.description: Upon picking up a certain amount of health, spawn a permanent angelic familiar.

414.name: More Options
414.description: Two item pedestals are presented in every Treasure Room. Only one can be taken; the other will disappear.

415.name: Crown Of Light
415.description: +2 Soul Hearts. While Isaac has no empty red hearts, grants 2x damage, increased range, and -0.3 shot speed. Regardless of health, the crown deactivates for the current room when Isaac takes damage.

416.name: Deep Pockets
416.description: Allows Isaac to carry two cards or pills (or a combination of both) at the same time. Increases the coin cap to 999. If a room would otherwise yield no reward, 1-3 coins will spawn.

417.name: Succubus
417.description: Spawns a flying familiar that bounces around the room with a black aura, dealing rapid damage to any enemies inside it. While standing in the aura, Isaac gains a 1.5x tear damage multiplier.

418.name: Fruit Cake
418.description: Isaac's tears gain a random effect that changes every shot.

419.name: Teleport 2.0
419.description: Teleports Isaac to a room that has not been explored yet. Normal rooms are prioritized over special rooms, and common special rooms take priority over rarer ones.

420.name: Black Powder
420.description: Isaac leaves a trail of black powder on the floor. Walking in a circle will spawn a pentagram symbol on the floor, which deals 10 damage per tick to any enemies inside it.

421.name: Kidney Bean
421.description: Isaac farts, charming all nearby enemies.

422.name: Glowing Hourglass
422.description: Rewinds time, putting Isaac back in the previous room and undoing anything that happened in the current room. Can only be used three times per floor, after which it functions like The Hourglass until the next floor.

423.name: Circle of Protection
423.description: Surrounds Isaac with a large white halo that occasionally deals Isaac's tear damage to enemies inside it, and can convert enemy shots into friendly homing tears.

424.name: Sack Head
424.description: Spawns a Grab Bag on pickup. Coins, Bombs, Keys, cards, runes and batteries have a chance to become Grab Bags.

425.name: Night Light
425.description: A cone of light shines in the direction Isaac is moving that slows enemies and enemy shots.

426.name: Obsessed Fan
426.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac's movements on a delay and deals 30 contact damage per second to enemies.

427.name: Mine Crafter
427.description: Places a Movable TNT barrel that can be pushed and used to destroy rocks or damage enemies. If used again in the same room while the previous TNT barrel is still intact, remotely detonates the TNT.

428.name: PJs
428.description: Grants 4 Soul Hearts and fully restores Isaac's health.

429.name: Head of the Keeper
429.description: Isaac's tears become coins and now have a chance to drop Pennies on the floor upon successfully hitting an enemy.

430.name: Papa Fly
430.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac's movements on a 3 second delay, firing tears at nearby enemies.

431.name: Multidimensional Baby
431.description: Spawns a familiar that will follow Isaac's movements on a 2.5-second delay. Tears that pass through the baby will be doubled and increase in speed.

432.name: Glitter Bombs
432.description: +5 Bombs. Bombs have a chance to drop random pickups or charm enemies when they explode.

433.name: My Shadow
433.description: Inflicts fear on all enemies in the room upon taking damage and spawns black friendly Chargers that attack enemies. Spawns a shadow familiar that closely follows behind Isaac. It spawns a black friendly Charger whenever an enemy touches it.

434.name: Jar of Flies
434.description: Killing an enemy adds a fly to the jar, up to a maximum of 20. On use, releases Blue Flies equal to the number of flies in the jar.

435.name: Lil Loki
435.description: Spawns a Loki familiar that follows Isaac and fires 4 tears in a cross pattern.

436.name: Milk!
436.description: Spawns a glass familiar that spills on the floor upon taking damage. After the milk spills, Isaac's tear delay is decreased by 2 for the current room. After the milk spills, Isaac's fire rate is increased by 1 for the current room.

437.name: D7
437.description: Restarts the current room and brings back all enemies, allowing more rewards to be acquired by completing the room.

438.name: Binky
438.description: Grants one Soul Heart, +0.75 tears and decreases Isaac's size.

439.name: Mom's Box
439.description: Increases luck by 1 and doubles the effects of trinkets while held. When used, drops a random trinket on the ground.

440.name: Kidney Stone
440.description: Randomly while firing tears, Isaac will stop firing and turn red, where he will charge and release a lot of 'tears' in one go. The burst of tears also includes a kidney stone, which deals a lot of damage.

441.name: Mega Blast
441.description: Isaac fires a giant laser for approximately 15 seconds. This laser deals massive damage, pushes Isaac backwards, and persists between rooms and floors.

442.name: Dark Prince's Crown
442.description: When at exactly one Red Heart, +0.75 tears, +1.5 range, and +0.2 shot speed. When at exactly one Red Heart, +2 fire rate, +1.5 range, and +0.2 shot speed.

443.name: Apple!
443.description: +0.3 tears. Adds a chance to fire a razor blade that deals 4× Isaac's damage.

444.name: Lead Pencil
444.description: After every 15 tears fired, Isaac will fire a high-damage cluster of tears.

445.name: Dog Tooth
445.description: +0.3 damage, +0.1 speed. Plays a howl or bark sound when entering a room with undiscovered Secret Rooms or Crawl Spaces.

446.name: Dead Tooth
446.description: While firing, Isaac gains a green aura that poisons nearby enemies.

447.name: Linger Bean
447.description: Constantly shooting causes Isaac to release gas clouds that can be pushed by his tears and damage nearby enemies.

448.name: Shard of Glass
448.description: Upon taking damage, Isaac has a chance to drop a full red heart, gain 5 range, and leave a trail of damaging red creep for the current room. Taking damage causes Isaac to bleed, spraying a volley of blood in the direction he fires. Bleeding will eventually damage him, but it can be stopped by picking up a Red Heart.

449.name: Metal Plate
449.description: Grants one Soul Heart. Enemy shots have a chance to be reflected at the shooter as confusing tears.

450.name: Eye of Greed
450.description: Every 20 tears, Isaac loses 1 Penny and shoots an additional gold tear that petrifies enemies and turns them into gold. Any enemy killed while in this state will drop coins.

451.name: Tarot Cloth
451.description: Drops a random card or rune. Doubles the effects of most cards and runes. Doubles the effects of tarot cards.

452.name: Varicose Veins
452.description: Taking damage releases a ring of 10 high damage tears.

453.name: Compound Fracture
453.description: Increases Range. Tears turn into bones, which shatter into 1-3 bone shards upon hitting an enemy or obstacle.

454.name: Polydactyly
454.description: Allows Isaac to carry two cards, pills, or any combination of both. Spawns one random card, rune, or pill.

455.name: Dad's Lost Coin
455.description: +1.5 range, +1 tear falling speed. Drops a Lucky Penny. +2.5 range. Drops a Lucky Penny.

456.name: Midnight Snack
456.description: Grants one full Red Heart container. Heals 1 additional Red Heart.

457.name: Cone Head
457.description: Grants a Soul Heart. Gives Isaac a chance to ignore any damage taken.

458.name: Belly Button
458.description: Drops a random trinket. Grants a second trinket slot.

459.name: Sinus Infection
459.description: Adds a chance to fire a booger that sticks to enemies and deals damage over time.

460.name: Glaucoma
460.description: Adds a chance to shoot tears that confuse enemies for an extremely long time.

461.name: Parasitoid
461.description: Adds a chance to fire an egg sack which creates slowing creep and spawns a Blue Fly or Blue Spider upon hitting an enemy.

462.name: Eye of Belial
462.description: Grants piercing tears. After piercing one enemy, tears start homing and deal double damage.

463.name: Sulfuric Acid
463.description: +0.3 damage. Adds a chance to fire acidic tears which can destroy obstacles and open doors.

464.name: Glyph of Balance
464.description: Grants 2 Soul Hearts and modifies drops from Champion monsters based on certain conditions. Also modifies room clear drops.

465.name: Analog Stick
465.description: +0.35 tears up. Allows Isaac to fire tears diagonally.

466.name: Contagion
466.description: The first enemy killed in a room releases a gas cloud that poisons nearby enemies. Affected enemies will also release gas upon death, spreading the effect.

467.name: Finger!
467.description: Spawns a finger familiar that faces in the same direction as Isaac, rapidly damaging enemies it points at for 10% of Isaac's damage.

468.name: Shade
468.description: Spawns a shadow familiar that follows Isaac's movements on a 1 second delay and deals contact damage to enemies. After dealing enough damage, it is absorbed by Isaac and spawns friendly Chargers.

469.name: Depression
469.description: Spawns a familiar that leaves a trail of creep that damages enemies at 6 damage per second. Has a chance to spawn damaging beams of light onto enemies that touch the cloud.

470.name: Hushy
470.description: Spawns a Hush familiar that bounces diagonally around the room and deals contact damage. While firing tears, it stops moving.

471.name: Lil Monstro
471.description: Spawns a familiar that fires clusters of tears. Must be charged before shooting.

472.name: King Baby
472.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac and makes other familiars follow it. While firing tears, other familiars stop moving.

473.name: Big Chubby
473.description: Spawns a familiar that follows Isaac and charges across the room when Isaac fires, blocking shots and dealing 40.5 damage per second on contact.

474.name: Broken Glass Cannon
474.description: Begins with no charges and turns into Glass Cannon when used. Only acquired by taking damage while holding Glass Cannon.

475.name: Plan C
475.description: Kills all enemies in the room, then kills Isaac three seconds later.

476.name: D1
476.description: Duplicates a random pickup in the room. The new pickup may be different than the original (i.e. a different card, etc).

477.name: Void
477.description: Consumes all pedestal items in the room. Active items will have their effects added to Void, and passive items will grant random stat upgrades.

478.name: Pause
478.description: Freezes all enemies until a fire button is pressed.

479.name: Smelter
479.description: Consumes Isaac's currently held trinket and applies its effect permanently.

480.name: Compost
480.description: Doubles Isaac's Blue Flies and Blue Spiders, or spawns one if Isaac has none. Converts pickups in the current room into Blue Flies or Blue Spiders.

481.name: Dataminer
481.description: Displaces enemy sprites for the current room, randomly increases one stat and decreases another.

482.name: Clicker
482.description: Transforms Isaac into a random character and removes the last item collected.

483.name: Mama Mega!
483.description: Damages all enemies and destroys all obstacles. The effect occurs every time a new room is entered for the rest of the floor. Opens the doors to the floor's Secret Rooms and Super Secret Rooms.

484.name: Wait What?
484.description: Isaac farts, sending out a circular rock wave that destroys obstacles and hurts enemies.
484.quote: I can't believe it's not butter bean!

485.name: Crooked Penny
485.description: Spawns a penny and has a 50% chance to double all items and pickups in the room. If the effect fails, the items and pickups disappear.

486.name: Dull Razor
486.description: Hurts Isaac without depleting health, activating any items that trigger upon taking damage.

487.name: Potato Peeler
487.description: Removes a Heart Container, increases damage and range, and grants a Cube of Meat.

488.name: Metronome
488.description: Grants a random item effect for the current room.

489.name: D infinity
489.description: Grants a random die item that changes each use. Acts as any die item, and can by cycled by pressing the drop key.

490.name: Eden's Soul
490.description: Spawns two item pedestals then is consumed. Begins with no charges.

491.name: Acid Baby
491.description: Spawns a familiar that drops a random pill every 3 rooms. Upon using a pill, all enemies in the room are poisoned.

492.name: YO LISTEN!
492.description: +1 luck. Spawns a fairy familiar that points out Secret Rooms, Crawl Space entrances, and tinted rocks.

493.name: Adrenaline
493.description: Increases damage based on how many empty Red Heart containers Isaac has.

494.name: Jacob's Ladder
494.description: Tears fire sparks of electricity in random directions upon hitting an obstacle or enemy.

495.name: Ghost Pepper
495.description: Gives a chance to shoot fires alongside tears that block enemy shots and deal damage to enemies that touch them. Gives a chance to shoot blue fires alongside tears that become smaller as they travel.

496.name: Euthanasia
496.description: Adds a luck-based chance to fire needles that instantly kill basic enemies and deal triple damage to bosses. If a needle kills an enemy, it bursts into more tears/needles.

497.name: Camo Undies
497.description: Isaac becomes camouflaged at the beginning of each room. Until he shoots, all non-boss enemies will be confused. Isaac gains +0.5 Speed while camouflaged, and gains Tears and Damage upon breaking it.

498.name: Duality
498.description: Whenever a Devil Room or Angel Room would spawn after defeating a boss, both rooms spawn. Only one can be entered.

499.name: Eucharist
499.description: An Angel Room will always spawn after every boss fight, excluding the first floor and floors after Chapter 4.

500.name: Sack of Sacks
500.description: Spawns a familiar that drops a Grab Bag every 5-6 rooms cleared.

501.name: Greed's Gullet
501.description: Grants a Red Heart container for every 25 Coins Isaac has.

502.name: Large Zit
502.description: Adds a chance to fire a creep shot that deals double damage and leaves a trail of slowing white creep.

503.name: Little Horn
503.description: Adds a chance to fire a piercing tear that instantly kills any enemy that it touches. Adds a chance to fire a tear that summons Big Horn 's hand to crush the first enemy it hits, instantly killing monsters or greatly damaging bosses.

504.name: Brown Nugget
504.description: Spawns a stationary fly turret that lasts for the current room and fires tears at nearby enemies.

505.name: Poke Go
505.description: Upon entering a room with enemies in it, has a chance to spawn a random friendly enemy that persists across rooms.

506.name: Backstabber
506.description: Isaac's tears deal double damage and inflict bleeding on enemies if they're facing away from Isaac.

507.name: Sharp Straw
507.description: Damages all enemies in the room. Has a chance to drop a Half Red Heart or Half Soul Heart if an enemy is hit. Damages all enemies in the room. Has a chance to drop a Half Red Heart if an enemy is hit.

508.name: Mom's Razor
508.description: Spawns an orbiting razor that deals contact damage and inflicts bleeding on enemies, causing them to slowly take damage over time.

509.name: Bloodshot Eye
509.description: Spawns an orbital familiar that deals 30 damage per second and fires a randomly angled tear every 2 seconds.

510.name: Delirious
510.description: Spawns Delirium as a random friendly boss that fights for Isaac.

511.name: Angry Fly
511.description: Spawns a fly familiar that orbits around a random enemy and deals 30 damage per second to enemies it comes in contact with.

512.name: Black Hole
512.description: Throws a black hole on the ground which sucks in and damages enemies and destroys nearby obstacles.

513.name: Bozo
513.description: +0.1 flat damage, grants a Soul Heart. Enemies can randomly become briefly charmed or feared. Taking damage has a chance to spawn a Rainbow Poop.

514.name: Broken Modem
514.description: Enemies, enemy shots, tears, and pickups will briefly freeze in place at random intervals. May also create alternative room rewards.

515.name: Mystery Gift
515.description: Spawns a random item from the current room's item pool, with a chance to spawn A Lump of Coal or The Poop instead.

516.name: Sprinkler
516.description: Creates a stationary sprinkler for the current room that rotates and fires tears in 8 directions. The tears copy Isaac's stats and most tear effects.

517.name: Fast Bombs
517.description: +7 Bombs. Removes the delay between bomb placements, allowing them to be placed rapidly. Bombs will no longer knock each other away.

518.name: Buddy in a Box
518.description: Spawns a familiar with a random tear effect. The familiar is randomized at the start of each floor.

519.name: Lil Delirium
519.description: Grants a familiar that transforms into another random familiar every 10 seconds.

520.name: Jumper Cables
520.description: Grants an active item charge every 15 enemies killed.

521.name: Coupon
521.description: While held, guarantees one item in every Shop will be on sale. On use, makes a random item in the current room free.

522.name: Telekinesis
522.description: Any enemy shots that come near Isaac for the next three seconds are held in place then fired back.

523.name: Moving Box
523.description: If the box is empty, picks up items and pickups in a room and stores them. If the box is not empty, places all stored items and pickups in the current room. Can carry up to 10 items or pickups at once.

524.name: Technology Zero
524.description: Connects Isaac's tears with electricity that can damage enemies.

525.name: Leprosy
525.description: Upon taking damage, grants a body part as an orbital, which blocks enemy shots and deals 7 damage per tick to enemies it comes in contact with. The orbitals will be destroyed if they take enough damage from enemies or enemy shots.

526.name: 7 Seals
526.description: Spawns a random Harbinger familiar that changes every 10 seconds. Harbingers have different behaviors and spawn themed Locusts.

527.name: Mr. ME!
527.description: Summons a controllable ghost that can perform various tasks depending on what it targets.

528.name: Angelic Prism
528.description: Spawns an orbital familiar with a large orbital radius. Tears that pass through the prism split into four multi-colored tears.

529.name: Pop!
529.description: Replaces Isaac's tears with eyeballs that can bounce off of each other. The eyeballs are not limited by range, and will instead dissipate when they stop moving or when hitting an enemy or obstacle.

530.name: Death's List
530.description: Grants a pickup or stat upgrade if all enemies in a room are killed in the order they are marked.

531.name: Haemolacria
531.description: Tears are now fired in an arc. Upon hitting the floor, an obstacle, or an enemy, they burst into many smaller tears in all directions. Increases tear delay.

532.name: Lachryphagy
532.description: Isaac's tears decelerate as they travel. Upon stopping or hitting an obstacle, they burst into 8 tears in all directions. Tears can be fired into other tears to feed them, increasing their damage.

533.name: Trisagion
533.description: Tears are replaced with piercing white blasts of light that deal less damage but can damage the same enemy multiple times.

534.name: Schoolbag
534.description: Allows Isaac to hold two active items.

535.name: Blanket
535.description: Grants one Soul Heart. Upon entering a boss room, grants a shield that blocks one hit, then disappears.

536.name: Sacrificial Altar
536.description: Sacrifices up to 2 familiars and spawns an item for each familiar sacrificed. Converts all friendly spiders and flies into coins.

537.name: Lil Spewer
537.description: Drops a random pill, and spawns a familiar that charges up and fires creep. Using pills changes the creep type.

538.name: Marbles
538.description: Spawns 3 random trinkets. Taking damage has a 5% chance to swallow Isaac's currently held trinket, gaining its effect permanently.

539.name: Mystery Egg
539.description: Spawns an egg familiar, which hatches a random friendly monster when Isaac is hurt once per room. The power of the monster improves for each consecutive room cleared without taking damage.

540.name: Flat Stone
540.description: Tears bounce off the floor, creating splashes. Splashes deal 25% of Isaac's tear damage to all enemies in a small area.

541.name: Marrow
541.description: Grants one Bone Heart and spawns three Red Hearts.

542.name: Slipped Rib
542.description: Spawns a bone familiar that circles around Isaac and reflects enemy shots.

543.name: Hallowed Ground
543.description: Spawns a white poop familiar, which turns into a White Poop when Isaac is hurt. White poop has an aura that increases tear fire rate and can block enemy shots. The aura also increases damage by 20% and gives homing.

544.name: Pointy Rib
544.description: Spawns a bone familiar that hovers back and forth in front of Isaac, dealing damage equal to Isaac's damage.

545.name: Book of the Dead
545.description: Creates a friendly Bony, Black Bony, or an orbital bone for each enemy killed in the current room. Creates a friendly Bony, Black Bony, Bone Fly, Revenant, or an orbital bone for each enemy killed in the current room.

546.name: Dad's Ring
546.description: Creates a ring of light around Isaac that petrifies enemies in contact.

547.name: Divorce Papers
547.description: Grants one Bone Heart, +0.7 tears, spawns a Mysterious Paper.

548.name: Jaw Bone
548.description: Spawns a familiar that flies through the room while firing, dealing a flat 7 contact damage to enemies and retrieving pickups.

549.name: Brittle Bones
549.description: Replaces all Red Heart Containers with 6 empty Bone Hearts. Upon losing a Bone Heart, Isaac fires bones in 8 directions and permanently gains a tears up. Upon losing a Bone Heart, Isaac fires bones in 8 directions and permanently gains a fire rate up.

550.name: Broken Shovel (Active)
550.description: While held, causes Mom to continuously attempt to stomp on Isaac. Activating makes her stop for the current room or wave. One of two parts necessary to create Mom's Shovel.

551.name: Broken Shovel (Passive)
551.description: One of two parts necessary to create Mom's Shovel. No effect if somehow obtained on its own.

552.name: Mom's Shovel
552.description: Creates a trapdoor that leads to the next floor. Unlocks The Forgotten when used on a mound of dirt that appears in Dark Room.

553.name: Mucormycosis
553.description: Gives Isaac the chance to fire spore tears that stick to enemies and blow up after a few seconds, dealing damage and poisoning nearby enemies and releasing more spores.

554.name: 2Spooky
554.description: Enemies near Isaac are afflicted with fear.

555.name: Golden Razor
555.description: Spends five Pennies to increase Isaac's damage by 1.2 for the current room.

556.name: Sulfur
556.description: Grants Brimstone for the current room.

557.name: Fortune Cookie
557.description: Gives Isaac a fortune, Soul Heart, Card, Rune, or trinket, similar to a Fortune Telling Machine. Fortunes are much more likely to be given than anything else.

558.name: Eye Sore
558.description: Causes Isaac to occasionally fire extra tears in random directions while shooting.

559.name: 120 Volt
559.description: Repeatedly zaps enemies that are close to Isaac.

560.name: It Hurts
560.description: Releases a ring of tears and increases fire rate for the current room when Isaac takes damage.

561.name: Almond Milk
561.description: Quadruples fire rate, with ×0.3 damage multiplier. Each tear is a given random effect that alters its movement.
561.quote: DMG down + tears up + you feel nutty

562.name: Rock Bottom
562.description: Locks Isaac's attributes to their highest values reached.

563.name: Nancy Bombs
563.description: +5 Bombs. Each bomb gains 1-4 random bomb synergies.

565.name: Blood Puppy
565.description: Spawns a familiar that chases enemies. After killing enough enemies, it becomes more powerful but will also try to hurt Isaac, it will also generate Half Red Hearts on enemy kills. It can increase in power one more stage after killing even more enemies. Dealing enough damage to it returns it to normal.

566.name: Dream Catcher
566.description: During the transition between floors, Isaac's nightmare shows the contents of the  upcoming floor's Treasure Room, as well as the floor's boss. Grants a Half Soul Heart when entering a new floor.

567.name: Paschal Candle
567.description: Gives Isaac a familiar that grants +0.4 Fire Rate for each consecutive room he's cleared without taking damage. The bonus stacks up to five times.

568.name: Divine Intervention
568.description: Double tapping a fire key creates a shield that pushes away enemies and reflects enemy projectiles and lasers.

569.name: Blood Oath
569.description: Stabs Isaac at the beginning of each floor, draining his Red Hearts. Increases damage and speed for the floor based on the amount drained.

570.name: Playdough Cookie
570.description: Grants multicolored tears. Each color comes with a different status or tear effect.

571.name: Orphan Socks
571.description: Prevents creep and floor spikes from damaging Isaac. Also gives Isaac +0.3 speed and 2 Soul Hearts.
571.quote: Speed up + your feet feel stronger

572.name: Eye of the Occult
572.description: +1 damage, +2 range, -0.16 shot speed. Isaac's tears can be controlled mid-flight with tear controls.
572.quote: DMG up + range up + controlled tears

573.name: Immaculate Heart
573.description: Adds one Red Heart Container and fully restores health. x1.2 damage multiplier. Isaac will occasionally fire extra tears that orbit around him.

574.name: Monstrance
574.description: Isaac gains an aura that deals damage to enemies inside it.

575.name: The Intruder
575.description: A familiar burrows in Isaac's head, firing 4 slowing tears. Upon taking damage, there's a chance it will burst out of Isaac's head, spawning blue spiders and chasing enemies for the current room.

576.name: Dirty Mind
576.description: Destroying poop spawns Dip Familiars that follow Isaac and damage enemies. Destroying different types of poop spawns different Dips with special effects.

577.name: Damocles
577.description: Spawns a sword above Isaac's head, which doubles all item pedestals. After Isaac takes damage, the sword can randomly fall at any point, instantly killing him.
577.quote: A king's fortune... but at what cost?

578.name: Free Lemonade
578.description: Creates a large pool of yellow creep beneath Isaac.

579.name: Spirit Sword
579.description: Instead of tears, Isaac swings a sword. Charging does a spin attack and fires a projectile, and a projectile is sometimes fired with normal swings if Isaac has no empty Red Heart Containers.

580.name: Red Key
580.description: Creates a Red Room adjacent to a viable wall, indicated by the outline of a door. These rooms have a 10% chance to be a special room.

581.name: Psy Fly
581.description: Spawns a fly orbital familiar that chases and blocks enemy shots.

582.name: Wavy Cap
582.description: Increases fire rate, decreases speed, and distorts the screen. All effects become more pronounced with repeated use, and wear off by clearing rooms.
582.quote: Tears up. A mind changing experience!

583.name: Rocket in a Jar
583.description: +5 Bombs. If Isaac is currently firing, placing a bomb will instead shoot a fast-moving, explosive rocket in the direction he's facing.

584.name: Book of Virtues
584.description: Spawns a destroyable orbiting wisp familiar that fires tears and deals contact damage. Also acts as a passive item that causes other active items to spawn themed wisps.

585.name: Alabaster Box
585.description: Spawns three Soul Hearts and two Angel Room items and is consumed. Starts with no charges, and can only be charged by picking up 6 Soul Hearts.

586.name: The Stairway
586.description: Generates a ladder at the start of every floor that leads to a unique Angel Room shop.
586.quote: May you get what you came for

588.name: Sol
588.description: Reveals the location of the Boss Room. Upon defeating a boss, activates XIX - The Sun, fully recharges Isaac's active item, grants bonus damage and luck for the rest of the floor, and removes curses.

589.name: Luna
589.description: Adds an extra Secret Room and Super Secret Room to each floor. Secret Rooms contain a beam of light that increases Fire Rate for the current floor and gives a Half Soul Heart.
589.quote: The moon's blessing shines upon you

590.name: Mercurius
590.description: +0.4 speed. Doors stay open after entering a room, even in rooms with enemies.

591.name: Venus
591.description: Adds one red Heart container. Heals 1 additional Red Heart. Enemies near Isaac become charmed.

592.name: Terra
592.description: +1 Damage. Replaces tears with rocks that deal variable damage, have increased knockback, and can destroy obstacles.

593.name: Mars
593.description: Dash by double-tapping the movement key, becoming invulnerable and damaging enemies. There's a short cooldown before Isaac can dash again.

594.name: Jupiter
594.description: +2 red Heart containers, -0.3 speed. Isaac builds speed while standing still, and releases poison gas clouds when he moves afterwards.

595.name: Saturnus
595.description: Upon entering a room, a circle of tears orbits Isaac. Enemy tears have a chance to be caught in orbit, turning them friendly.

596.name: Uranus
596.description: Isaac shoots ice tears, which slow enemies and freeze monsters they kill. Frozen enemies slide away and explode into ice shards when touched.

597.name: Neptunus
597.description: Isaac's mouth fills with tears over time while not firing, up to a cap. Holding the fire button will release all stored tears in rapid succession.

598.name: Pluto
598.description: +0.7 tears. Significantly shrinks Isaac, allowing him to squeeze between objects and makes some enemy shots pass over him.

599.name: Voodoo Head
599.description: Spawns an additional Curse Room on each floor. Curse Rooms have improved layouts.

600.name: Eye Drops
600.description: Increases the fire rate in Isaac's left eye, causing his eyes to fire at different rates.

601.name: Act of Contrition
601.description: +0.7 tears, grants an Eternal Heart. Allows Angel Rooms to appear even if a Devil Deal has been taken before. Reduces the Devil/Angel room chance penalty for taking Red heart damage.

602.name: Member Card
602.description: Adds a trapdoor to every Shop that leads to a second shop with a unique stock and marked-up prices.

603.name: Battery Pack
603.description: Recharges Isaac's currently held active item and drops 2-4 batteries.

604.name: Mom's Bracelet
604.description: Lets Isaac pick up and throw rocks, TNT, Poops, friendly Dips, Bombs, and other obstacles.

605.name: The Scooper
605.description: Summons The Peeper for the current room, which leaves a trail of red creep.

606.name: Ocular Rift
606.description: Adds a chance to fire tears that create rifts where they land, which suck enemies, pickups, and shots towards them and damage enemies in the area.

607.name: Boiled Baby
607.description: Gives Isaac a familiar that fires chaotic bursts of tears in all directions.

608.name: Freezer Baby
608.description: Spawns a shooting familiar that has a chance to petrify enemies, and freezes monsters upon killing them.

609.name: Eternal D6
609.description: Rerolls all items in the room. Each item has a 25% chance to disappear instead.

610.name: Bird Cage
610.description: The first time Isaac takes damage in a room, a familiar leaps on an enemy, dealing damage and releasing a rock wave. For the rest of the room, it chases enemies similar to Dead Bird.

611.name: Larynx
611.description: Isaac shouts, damaging and pushing away nearby enemies. The shout gets stronger the more charges the item has. Larynx gains 1 charge whenever Isaac takes damage, in addition to charging normally.

612.name: Lost Soul
612.description: Creates a ghostly familiar that closely follows behind Isaac. It dies in one hit, but respawns at the start of the next floor. Each time it survives until the next floor, it rewards Isaac with Soul Hearts, Eternal Hearts, or an Item.

614.name: Blood Bombs
614.description: Grants a Red Heart container and restores 5 hearts. Bombs leave behind damaging red creep. Isaac can place Bombs at the cost of half a heart if he doesn't have any.

615.name: Lil Dumpy
615.description: Spawns a Dumpy familiar that pushes away nearby enemies and projectiles just before Isaac is about to be hit, then falls asleep. He can be awoken by walking to him.

616.name: Bird's Eye
616.description: Gives a chance to shoot fires alongside tears that block enemy shots and deal damage to enemies that touch them.

617.name: Lodestone
617.description: Gives Isaac the chance to fire tears that magnetize enemies they hit, causing them to attract nearby pickups and enemies, as well as tears/shots from all sources.

618.name: Rotten Tomato
618.description: Adds a chance to fire tears that mark enemies with the Bait status effect. Enemies marked as bait are attacked by other enemies.

619.name: Birthright
619.description: Grants a character -specific effect that enhances their special abilities.

621.name: Red Stew
621.description: Refills all heart containers. Grants an enormous damage boost that wears off over time.

622.name: Genesis
622.description: Removes all of Isaac's items and pickups and takes him to a unique Bedroom with some pickups and Chests and a trapdoor to the next floor. For every item Isaac lost, he gets to take an item from a set of three.

623.name: Sharp Key
623.description: Adds 5 Keys on pickup. Allows Isaac to throw his keys to deal damage to enemies, destroy obstacles, and open doors.

625.name: Mega Mush
625.description: Gigantifies Isaac for 30 seconds, increasing damage and range while lowering tears, granting invulnerability, and allowing Isaac to crush enemies and obstacles he walks on. The effect persists between rooms.

626.name: Knife Piece 1
626.description: Combined with Knife Piece 2, creates a knife familiar that damages enemies and can open the door to the Corpse.

627.name: Knife Piece 2
627.description: Combined with Knife Piece 1, creates a knife familiar that damages enemies and can open the door to the Corpse.

628.name: Death Certificate
628.description: Takes Isaac to an abandoned and expanded version of Home, which has one copy of every item in the game. After taking an item, Isaac returns to the room he used Death Certificate in.

629.name: Bot Fly
629.description: Spawns an orbiting fly familiar that fires shielded tears at incoming enemy projectiles.

631.name: Meat Cleaver
631.description: Splits all enemies in the room into two smaller versions of themselves with much less health.

632.name: Evil Charm
632.description: +2 luck. Provides immunity to burn, confusion, fear, and poison.

633.name: Dogma
633.description: Grants flight, +2 damage, and increases speed to 1.1. Grants enough health to have 6 full hearts, if possible. Grants the Holy Mantle effect for the room it was obtained in. Automatically given to Isaac after defeating Dogma.

634.name: Purgatory
634.description: While in a room with enemies, spawns red cracks in the ground. Walking over these cracks summons ghosts that launch themselves at enemies and explode.

635.name: Stitches
635.description: Passively spawns a familiar that moves in the direction Isaac shoots. On use, Isaac swaps places with the familiar.

636.name: R Key
636.description: Brings Isaac back to the first floor of a new run, retaining all of his items.

637.name: Knockout Drops
637.description: Adds a chance to shoot a fist tear that has extremely high knockback and confuses enemies.

638.name: Eraser
638.description: Throws an eraser that instantly kills the first monster it hits, and prevents that monster from spawning for the rest of the run. Deals 15 damage to bosses, erasing that boss if fatal. Can only be used once per floor.

640.name: Urn of Souls
640.description: Spews a stream of damaging flame. Gains Soul Charges each time an enemy dies, which are used to fuel the urn.

641.name: Akeldama
641.description: While in an uncleared room, Isaac forms a trail of bloody tears that drags behind him, bursting and dealing damage upon contact with enemies.

642.name: Magic Skin
642.description: Consumes one heart container or two Soul Hearts to spawn an item and give Isaac a broken heart container that can never be filled. If Magic Skin isn't being held after being used, it is very likely to replace any future items.

643.name: Revelation
643.description: Grants flight and two Soul Hearts. In addition to tears, Isaac can charge up and fire a powerful holy laser.

644.name: Consolation Prize
644.description: Increases Isaac's lowest stat and drops either 3 Coins, 1 Bomb, or 1 Key depending on what Isaac has the least of.

645.name: Tinytoma
645.description: Gives Isaac a Teratoma orbital that blocks shots, deals contact damage, and splits into smaller versions of itself upon taking damage. The smaller versions break into blue spiders.

646.name: Brimstone Bombs
646.description: +5 Bombs. Bombs fire four Brimstone lasers in the cardinal directions upon exploding.

647.name: 4.5 Volt
647.description: Active items don't charge when clearing rooms. Instead, they're charged by dealing damage to enemies.
647.quote: Beat the juice out of them!

649.name: Fruity Plum
649.description: Gives Isaac a miniature Baby Plum familiar that propels itself diagonally around the room, firing tears behind itself as it travels.

650.name: Plum Flute
650.description: Summons the boss Baby Plum to fight for Isaac in the current room.

651.name: Star of Bethlehem
651.description: Spawns a star familiar that slowly travels towards the Boss Room, giving an aura that increases damage and tears and grants homing tears.

652.name: Cube Baby
652.description: Spawns an ice cube familiar that slides around when walked into. It slows and deals contact damage, freezing monsters it kills.

653.name: Vade Retro
653.description: While held, enemies leave behind ghosts on death. Stronger enemies leave bigger ghosts. Using the item causes the ghosts to explode and damage nearby enemies, and instantly kills all ghost enemies with less than 50% HP.

654.name: False PHD
654.description: Converts good pills into bad pills and identifies all pills. Bad pills now have secondary positive effects. Grants one Black Heart.

655.name: Spin to Win
655.description: Gives +0.5 speed and greatly increases the rotation speed and damage of orbitals for 3 seconds. Passively gives Isaac a spinning top orbital that blocks enemy shots and deals contact damage.

657.name: Vasculitis
657.description: Enemies explode into tears upon death, which inherit the effects of Isaac's tears.

658.name: Giant Cell
658.description: Causes Isaac to spawn Minisaac familiars when he takes damage, which chase and shoot at nearby enemies.

660.name: Card Reading
660.description: Spawns two portals at the beginning of each floor that each lead to either the Boss Room, Treasure Room, or Secret Room.

661.name: Quints
661.description: The first five enemies killed in a room will spawn stationary shooting familiars where they died.

663.name: Tooth and Nail
663.description: Isaac periodically turns into a spiked statue, briefly becoming invulnerable and dealing contact damage.

664.name: Binge Eater
664.description: +1 Red Heart Container and fully heals Isaac. Item pedestals also offer a random food item. Picking up a food item temporarily grants +3.6 damage and permanently boosts 2 stats.

665.name: Guppy's Eye
665.description: Shows the contents of Chests, Fire Places, Grab Bags, and Shopkeepers before they're opened/destroyed.

667.name: Strawman
667.description: Spawns a controllable Keeper to fight enemies alongside Isaac, functioning similarly to Jacob and Esau. If Keeper dies, he spawns 5 blue spiders and Strawman is removed from Isaac's inventory.

668.name: Dad's Note
668.description: Sends Isaac on an Ascent toward Home.

669.name: Sausage
669.description: Adds a Red Heart Container, fully heals Isaac, and gives +0.2 Speed, +0.5 Damage, +0.5 Tears, +2.5 Range, +0.2 Shot Speed, and +1.0 Luck. Increases the chance of encountering a Devil Room, Angel Room, and/or Planetarium each by 6.9%.

670.name: Options?
670.description: If a room gives a reward when cleared, there will be two different rewards to chose from. Taking one causes the other to disappear.

671.name: Candy Heart
671.description: Gives Isaac a permanent stat boost whenever he heals with Red Heart pickups.

672.name: A Pound of Flesh
672.description: Devil deals now cost Coins, Shop items now cost health, and consumables in shops are free but surrounded by spikes.

673.name: Redemption
673.description: If Isaac enters a Devil Room but leaves without taking/opening anything in it, he gets +1 Damage and a Soul Heart at the start of the next floor.

674.name: Spirit Shackles
674.description: On death, Isaac's ghost is chained to his dead body and he can continue to fight with 1/2 of a heart, returning to life after 10 seconds. After it activates, it must be recharged by picking up a Soul Heart.

675.name: Cracked Orb
675.description: Unlocks doors and reveals a random room on the map when Isaac takes damage.

676.name: Empty Heart
676.description: If Isaac has one red heart or fewer at the beginning of a floor, he gains an empty red heart container.

677.name: Astral Projection
677.description: Causes Isaac to turn into a ghost if he gets hit while in an uncleared room, giving him flight and spectral tears and blocking the next hit he takes.

678.name: C Section
678.description: Replaces tears with fetuses that chase down enemies and deal contact damage. Each shot requires a brief charge up.

679.name: Lil Abaddon
679.description: Spawns a familiar that charges a miniature Maw Of The Void attack while Isaac shoots.

680.name: Montezuma's Revenge
680.description: While firing, Isaac charges up a short-ranged Brimstone -like diarrhea beam that shoots behind him.

681.name: Lil Portal
681.description: A familiar that flies forward, consuming pickups in its path. Each one will increase its size and damage and spawn a Blue Fly. Every four pickups, it opens a portal that leads to an unexplored room.

682.name: Worm Friend
682.description: Gives Isaac a Nerve Ending familiar that burrows out of the ground to grab and deal damage to enemies over time.

683.name: Bone Spurs
683.description: Enemies spawn floating bones on death, which block shots and damage/repel enemies that touch them.

684.name: Hungry Soul
684.description: Enemies have a chance to spawn ghosts on death, which chase and deal contact damage to enemies and explode after a short time.

685.name: Jar of Wisps
685.description: Spawns random wisps that shoot various tears, block shots, and deal contact damage. The number of wisps spawned increases every time the jar is used.

686.name: Soul Locket
686.description: Gives Isaac a permanent stat boost whenever he picks up a Soul Heart.

687.name: Friend Finder
687.description: Spawns a random friendly monster that mimics Isaac's movements and attacks.

688.name: Inner Child
688.description: Upon death, Isaac respawns in the current room with half of a Red Heart, a massive size down, and +0.2 Speed.

689.name: Glitched Crown
689.description: Item pedestals cycle between 5 random items before being picked up.

690.name: Belly Jelly
690.description: Causes enemies to bounce off of Isaac, dealing damage to them if they hit an enemy or obstacle. Also gives Isaac the chance to deflect enemy shots.

691.name: Sacred Orb
691.description: Prevents items of quality 0-1 from appearing, and items of quality 2 from appearing 33% of the time, greatly increasing the quality of items received from all item pools. Quest items are unaffected.

692.name: Sanguine Bond
692.description: Spawns a special set of spikes in the Devil Room. Taking damage from the spikes has a chance to grant a reward.

693.name: The Swarm
693.description: Spawns eight orbital flies, which turn into Blue Flies after they block a shot. Each time a room is cleared, spawns another orbital fly.

694.name: Heartbreak
694.description: Grants 3 broken hearts and +0.25 damage for every broken heart Isaac has. Every otherwise fatal hit will add 2 more until Isaac has nothing but broken hearts.

695.name: Bloody Gust
695.description: The first 6 times Isaac takes damage on a given floor, he gains Speed and Fire Rate for the rest of the floor, up to a maximum of +1.02 and +3.00, respectively.

696.name: Salvation
696.description: Gives Isaac a halo that summons beams of light on enemies inside it. The halo grows larger the more times Isaac has taken damage this floor.

697.name: Vanishing Twin
697.description: Spawns a familiar that becomes a weaker clone of the floor's boss when entering the Boss Room. Defeating it drops an extra item.

698.name: Twisted Pair
698.description: Spawns two familiars that float on either side of Isaac and fire tears that use his tears, range, shot speed, and tear effects, and scale with damage.

699.name: Azazel's Rage
699.description: Isaac builds rage every time a room is cleared. After four rooms, fires a large Brimstone laser when entering the next room.

700.name: Echo Chamber
700.description: When Isaac uses a Card, Pill, or Rune, he also uses a copy of the previous three Cards/Pills/Runes he used after picking up Echo Chamber.
700.quote: I can see see the future future future

701.name: Isaac's Tomb
701.description: Spawns an Old Chest at the start of each floor.

702.name: Vengeful Spirit
702.description: After taking damage, spawns an orbital wisp that lasts for the entire floor, up to a maximum of six. They fire tears but do not block shots.

703.name: Esau Jr.
703.description: Swaps between the current character and Esau Jr., who has +2 flat damage and flight. Characters have independent items and health. Dying as either character ends the run.

704.name: Berserk!
704.description: Isaac goes berserk for 5 seconds, greatly increasing his speed, tears, and damage, but restricting him to using a melee weapon instead of his tears. This item charges by dealing damage to enemies instead of clearing rooms.

705.name: Dark Arts
705.description: Briefly grants +1 speed and makes Isaac invulnerable and intangible. When the effect ends, destroys all projectiles and damages all enemies Isaac ran through.

706.name: Abyss
706.description: Destroys all items in the room and gives Isaac a unique locust familiar for each item destroyed. Some items generate locusts with special effects.

707.name: Supper
707.description: Grants one full Red Heart container. Heals 1 additional Red Heart.

708.name: Stapler
708.description: +1 Damage. Prevents Isaac from firing tears from his left eye, like Cain.

709.name: Suplex!
709.description: Isaac dashes forward and picks up the first enemy hit. After a moment, he slams them into the ground to deal damage and create a circular rock wave.

710.name: Bag of Crafting
710.description: Collects and holds up to 8 pickups, which can then be used to craft an item. The power level of the item is based on the quality of pickups used.

711.name: Flip
711.description: Item pedestals have a second uninteractable "ghostly" item behind them. Activating will flip the real and ghostly items around. If playing as Tainted Lazarus, also flips between them and Dead Tainted Lazarus.

712.name: Lemegeton
712.description: Spawns a wisp representing a random passive item, which orbits Isaac but can be destroyed. While the wisp is alive, Isaac gains that item's effects. Generation uses the current room's item pool 25% of the time, otherwise a random pool.

713.name: Sumptorium
713.description: Removes half a heart and creates a Clot familiar that mimics Isaac's movements and tear effects. As Tainted Eve, passively converts health into Clots while firing. Activating returns all Clots to health.

714.name: Recall
714.description: Retrieves the Forgotten's body from any distance. Only available as the Birthright effect for Tainted Forgotten.

715.name: Hold
715.description: Exclusive to Tainted ???. Allows him to save one poop bomb for later, allowing him to gather more over time.

716.name: Keeper's Sack
716.description: Gives range, speed, or damage when buying things from a shop. Also spawns three coins and a Key on pickup.

717.name: Keeper's Kin
717.description: Rocks and other Obstacles spawn blue spiders over time while in a room with enemies, and spawn two blue spiders when destroyed.

719.name: Keeper's Box
719.description: Spawns a random shop item or pickup which can be bought for its normal price.

720.name: Everything Jar
720.description: Spawns certain pickups based on how many charges it has. If fully charged, instead has one of many unique effects.

721.name: TMTRAINER
721.description: Causes all future items to be "glitched", granting them completely random effects.
721.quote: ZZaZZ ZZdZZiZZmZZhZZ ZZvZZ ZZoZZ ZZ ZZsZZlZZhZZsZZoZZaZZiZZ

722.name: Anima Sola
722.description: Chains down the nearest enemy for 5 seconds, preventing them from acting.

723.name: Spindown Dice
723.description: Reduces the internal ID number of all items in the room by one, turning them into the item with that number.

724.name: Hypercoagulation
724.description: After Isaac takes damage from an enemy or donates health, launches Red Hearts from Isaac that despawn after 1.5 seconds.

725.name: IBS
725.description: Causes Isaac to throw poop, create buffing creep, or drop bombs while fighting enemies.

726.name: Hemoptysis
726.description: Double-tapping a fire button causes Isaac to sneeze blood, dealing damage to enemies in front of him. Affected enemies are cursed and take more damage from Brimstone -like attacks.

727.name: Ghost Bombs
727.description: +5 Bombs. Bombs become spectral and spawn ghosts that deal contact damage to enemies and explode after 10 seconds.

728.name: Gello
728.description: Spawns a demon familiar for the current room that's attached to Isaac and moves and fires in the direction Isaac shoots, using Isaac's damage, tears, range, shot speed, and special tear effects.

729.name: Decap Attack
729.description: Throws Isaac's head, which is still able to fire tears at the spot it lands. Reactivating the item or stepping on the head reattaches it.

731.name: Stye
731.description: Tears fired from Isaac's right eye have +28% Damage, +6.5 Range, and -0.3 Shot Speed.

732.name: Mom's Ring
732.description: +1 Damage. Drops a random Rune or Soul Stone upon pickup.
